title: RCA 480P LCD Home Theater
description: View your favorite movies and TV shows on the big screen with this RCA home theatre projector. It projects onto any flat surface and delivers a screen size from 30" all the way up to a 130" for an immersive viewing experience. It boasts two HDMI ports so you can easily connect gaming consoles, Blu-ray players, streaming devices, and more. 480p resolution, but supports 1080p with HDMI connection. Built-in speakers and exceptional picture quality for movies and gaming. Estimated 50,000 hour lamp life or 5.7 years with 24 hours a day viewing.
